Name: Thonet Side Chair, Oak
Description: Made from solid oak with a stunning, visible grain, the Thonet Side Chair from 4orm4 seamlessly combines practicality with captivating design. Lightweight and easy to maneuver, this chair sports a bent wood construction that highlights its Thonet-inspired bistro allure paired with a hint of rustic elegance. The rounded cane seat offers both comfort and style, making it a versatile gem for dining rooms and kitchens. The oak's light finish fits beautifully with various decor themes, while the open back design brings an airy, uncluttered vibe to any space. Perfect for everyday use, this chair is more than just furniture‚Äîit's a celebration of timeless design and exceptional craftsmanship.

Name: Trio Side Table, Ash
Description: Made from solid ash and featuring elegant traditional turnings, the Trio Side Table blends modern style with the rich design heritage of the 20th century. This versatile table fits seamlessly into both vintage-inspired settings and modern spaces. Built with three sturdy stretchers for lasting stability, it's a dependable piece that can serve as an end table or a plant stand, perfect for your living room, sunroom, office, or bedroom.

Name: Tay Chair, Midnight Black Premium Leather
Description: The Tay Chair boasts a sleek and bold design that's sure to catch the eye. Its clean lines and solid build make a statement, while the angular legs are artfully balanced by a curved backrest crafted for comfort. Upholstered in luxuriously smooth Italian aniline leather, this chair exudes quality. The leather's natural elegance is enhanced by a powder-coated metal finish, offering exceptional durability against everyday wear and tear. Named for the distinct 'T' shape formed at the intersection of its metal legs and backrest, the Tay Chair embodies simplicity and elegance, making it a perfect fit for any chic, unfussy interior. Brought to you by 4orm4, this chair promises both longevity and timeless style.

Name: Shaker Armchair, Walnut
Description: The Shaker Armchair beautifully captures the essence of mid-century modern design, celebrated for its graceful simplicity and comfort that fits naturally with the human form. Inspired by the Shaker tradition, which is renowned for its straightforward elegance, crisp lines, and practical allure, this chair radiates a timeless charm. At the same time, it offers a fresh, modern twist on these classic design principles.

Name: Rose Dining Chair, Mushroom Velvet and Walnut
Description: Discover the exquisite elegance of the Rose Dining Chair, brought to you by 4orm4. This chair represents the perfect blend of contemporary style and classic allure, elevating it beyond mere functionality to a true statement of sophistication and comfort. At the heart of its design is a strong yet graceful walnut frame, radiating warmth and charm with each beautiful curve. The rich, natural tones of the walnut wood introduce a hint of opulence to any dining area, enhancing the overall sense of refined luxury. The arms are thoughtfully contoured and elegantly sculpted, offering both visual allure and exceptional support, inviting you to sit back, relax, and enjoy each moment to the fullest.

Name: Poet Sofa, Wheat Gray Cashmere Wool
Description: The Poet Sofa is a charming piece inspired by the mid-century Danish design, featuring a soft and inviting gray wool upholstery in warm tones. Its sculptural form, complemented by gentle curves, creates a cozy and intimate atmosphere, making it both eye-catching and welcoming for anyone who takes a seat. The backrest is adorned with button detailing that adds a touch of elegance, while the rounded club legs crafted from dark wood provide a secure and stylish base. This sofa is a perfect fit for any modern interior, seamlessly blending form with function. Its sleek, minimalist design makes it an excellent choice for those seeking to enhance their space with a piece that delivers both comfort and a nod to timeless mid-century charm.

Name: Porto Table Lamp, Portable, Gold
Description: The Porto Table Lamp from 4orm4 beautifully merges modern style with practical design, making it a versatile addition to any space. This lamp is characterized by its sleek lines and minimalist profile, providing not just light, but also an eye-catching accent that easily fits into a range of interior d√©cors. Its unique design prioritizes both simplicity and sophistication. Meticulously crafted, every part of this lamp adds to its visual charm. From the thoughtfully chosen materials for the base, shade, and handle, to its cohesive and elegant design, the Porto Table Lamp enhances the atmosphere of any room it graces.

Name: PK22 Lounge Chair, Natural Rattan
Description: The PK22 Chair is a true classic in Danish design, revered for its sleek, minimalist elegance and outstanding craftsmanship. Drawing inspiration from the iconic styles of the 1950s, this chair perfectly captures the spirit of Scandinavian modernism with its neat lines, practical form, and top-quality materials. The PK22 is known for its straightforward design and practicality. Its lightweight frame and minimalist silhouette make it incredibly flexible and suitable for a wide range of settings, whether in homes, offices, or public areas. Its enduring design keeps it a favorite among design enthusiasts, remaining stylish and sought-after through the years.

Name: Papa Bear Lounge Chair, Indigo Blue Wool
Description: Meet the Papa Bear Chair, a true gem of mid-century modern design crafted by 4orm4. This chair beautifully combines style, expert craftsmanship, and ultimate comfort. An emblem of mid-century modern aesthetics and luxurious coziness, it's an ideal centerpiece for any living area, whether your space is contemporary or timeless.

Name: Papa Bear Ottoman, Light Gray Wool and Walnut
Description: Meet the Papa Bear Ottoman, a perfect partner to the renowned mid-century modern chair, lovingly crafted by 4orm4. This outstanding ottoman is a harmonious blend of timeless style, expert craftsmanship, and indulgent comfort. It embodies the essence of mid-century modern design while offering unmatched warmth, effortlessly enhancing both contemporary and traditional living areas.

Name: Ox Ottoman, Wheat Gray Cashmere Wool
Description: Add the perfect finishing touch to your seating area with the Ox Ottoman. Taking cues from mid-century Scandinavian design, this ottoman brings a sense of enduring elegance and refinement to any room. Its chic and streamlined shape combined with exceptional comfort is sure to enhance your living space.

Name: Ox Chair, Wheat Gray Cashmere Wool
Description: The Ox Chair, inspired by the classic mid-century Scandinavian design, beautifully captures the timeless appeal of enduring aesthetics. Known for its striking, sculptural shape and unmatched comfort, the Ox Chair epitomizes modern sophistication. Crafted with the utmost attention to detail, it exemplifies a perfect balance of form and function. Its unique silhouette, defined by flowing curves and sharp angles, conveys a feeling of dynamic motion and natural elegance.

Name: Orielle Suspension Light, Small, Tan and Brass
Description: Brighten up your home with the Orielle Suspension Light from 4orm4, a contemporary gem that charms with its distinctive design and outstanding functionality. Meticulously crafted, this ceiling light embodies modern aesthetics, effortlessly merging minimalist elegance with practical use. With various sizes to choose from, the Orielle Suspension Light caters to different spaces and design tastes. Whether you wish to make a bold statement or prefer a subtle touch, you'll find just the right size for your space. Opt for the Orielle Suspension Light alone for a sleek and minimalist vibe, or mix several together in creative arrangements for a breathtaking visual effect.

It beautifully marries form and function, presenting a look that's as captivating as it is practical. Its sleek, organic lines and minimalist style make it a visual delight, while its glow brings warmth and a welcoming vibe to any space. Whether used as a charming focal point or a functional light, this lamp adds both elegance and coziness to your surroundings.

Name: Oka Ceiling Lamp, Black and Natural Rattan
Description: Discover the Oka Ceiling Lamp, a perfect blend of traditional craftsmanship and modern design with hints of Asian inspiration, brought to you by 4orm4. This exquisite piece is masterfully crafted to become a true standout in any room. Its most captivating feature is the cane diffuser, an elegant nod to the enduring art of caning. Whether adorning your living room, dining area, or bedroom, this lamp envelops your surroundings with a soft, inviting light, creating a welcoming atmosphere for any moment.

Name: Noom Dining Table, Light Oak, 201cm
Description: The Noom Dining Table is a beautifully crafted piece that brings a modern yet elegant vibe to any dining room. Made from oak with a light finish, it showcases solid oak legs with a unique deep curve, creating a flat base that gracefully supports the tabletop. The tabletop is designed with a chamfered edge, adding to the table‚Äôs clean and straightforward appeal. This table comfortably seats six, and can accommodate up to eight, making it ideal for cozy dinners or larger gatherings alike. The lovely oak veneer surface adds a dash of natural charm, making it the perfect centerpiece for any dining area. For a cohesive Scandinavian-inspired look, pair this table with fabric chairs in soothing, neutral colors, or choose darker chairs to create a sophisticated contrast.

Name: Mia Loveseat, Wheat Gray Cashmere Wool
Description:
The Mia Loveseat is where contemporary flair meets supreme comfort. This piece showcases a deeply cushioned seat, paired with a padded backrest and arms that feature expertly pulled corners, creating a plush, pillow-like sensation. The inviting mid-toned grey upholstery serves as a neutral canvas, effortlessly warming up any room. Subtle piping accents along the arms and backrest add to its stylish appeal, highlighting its clean lines.

With a higher seat-to-back ratio, the Mia Loveseat provides a supportive, cozy seating experience, all wrapped up in a sleek, modern silhouette. Its low-profile legs offer a discreet charm, ensuring that the minimalist design takes center stage. It's the perfect fit for any contemporary living space, seamlessly blending in while offering undeniable style and comfort.

Name: Mario Bellini Two Seater Sofa, Tan Vegan Leather
Description:
Dive into the nostalgic charm of the 1970s with the Bellini, a sectional that offers both flexibility and a refreshing departure from bulky furniture styles. Perfect for open-plan living, this modern beauty allows you to transform your space according to your mood and needs, without the hassle of redecorating.

Once again adored by a new generation of furniture enthusiasts, the Bellini is celebrated for its versatility and liberating design. Thanks to its tie rods and rings, you can effortlessly detach and rearrange its modules, giving you the freedom to tailor the sofa to your changing tastes and whims.

Built with a sturdy wooden frame and cushioned with cold-pressed foam that's enveloped in a soft fabric, this low-profile piece embodies relaxed luxury. Each plush cushion invites you to sink in and unwind, making it the perfect spot to lounge in style.

Dive into the nostalgic charm of the 1970s with the Bellini, a sectional that offers both flexibility and a refreshing departure from bulky furniture styles. Perfect for open-plan living, this modern beauty allows you to transform your space according to your mood and needs, without the hassle of redecorating.

Once again adored by a new generation of furniture enthusiasts, the Bellini is celebrated for its versatility and liberating design. Thanks to its tie rods and rings, you can effortlessly detach and rearrange its modules, giving you the freedom to tailor the sofa to your changing tastes and whims.

Built with a sturdy wooden frame and cushioned with cold-pressed foam that's enveloped in a soft fabric, this low-profile piece embodies relaxed luxury. Each plush cushion invites you to sink in and unwind, making it the perfect spot to lounge in style.

Step back into the vibe of the 1970s with the Bellini Sectional Sofa, designed for those who appreciate the freedom of open-plan living. Rediscovered and cherished by the latest generation of design enthusiasts, the Bellini is once again celebrated for its flexibility and sense of liberation. Name: Loki Table, Black Ash
Description: Introducing the Loki Table from 4orm4, a standout piece that brings a unique flair to any room with its eye-catching fan-shaped top. This table captures the spirit of the 1970s, all while offering a design that's truly timeless and stylish. Its blend of classic and modern vibes makes it a perfect addition to contemporary interiors, lending a hint of vintage allure without sacrificing modern aesthetics. More than just a pretty piece, the Loki Table is a harmonious blend of style and practicality. Whether you're hosting a dinner or diving into a creative task, this table serves as both a functional and elegant surface. It's an essential touch of sophistication for both your home and office spaces.

Name: Jura Armchair, Indigo Blue Wool
Description:
The Jura Lounge Chair is a remarkable piece that embodies the timeless elegance of classic mid-century Danish design. With its distinctive boxy profile and polished steel runners that gracefully wrap around the arms and integrate smoothly into the frame, this chair brings a modern touch of sophistication to any setting. The rich, vibrant blue wool upholstery creates a striking contrast with the shimmering metal details, while the thick foam-cushioned seat promises exceptional comfort.

Whether you're looking for a standout piece or want to complement a mid-century inspired interior, the Jura Lounge Chair from 4orm4 is the perfect choice. Its robust wooden internal frame ensures it stands the test of time, while the luxurious wool fabric combined with minimalist metal legs strikes the perfect balance of comfort and style. This makes it a versatile addition to both cozy homes and dynamic commercial spaces.

Name: IC S2 Pendant Light, Pewter
Description: Drawing inspiration from the poise and skill of a masterful juggler, the IC S2 Ceiling Light by 4orm4 beautifully captures the theme of balance with subtle elegance. This pendant light features an art deco-inspired opal glass orb that appears to float effortlessly against its metal bracket, creating a delightful illusion. With its simple yet striking design, the IC Lights collection celebrates the artistry that emerges from pure inspiration, premium materials, and minimalistic aesthetics.

Name: Husk Lounge Chair, Wheat Gray Cashmere Wool
Description:
The Husk Lounge Chair boasts a distinctive design that beautifully marries comfort with modern sophistication. Wrapped in a cozy, mid-tone grey wool, its padded foam compartments are accentuated by meticulous stitch-work, creating a welcoming, cocoon-like embrace. Perfect for open-plan living, this modern beauty allows you to transform your space according to your mood and needs, without the hassle of redecorating.

Once again adored by a new generation of furniture enthusiasts, the Bellini is celebrated for its versatility and liberating design. Thanks to its tie rods and rings, you can effortlessly detach and rearrange its modules, giving you the freedom to tailor the sofa to your changing tastes and whims.

Built with a sturdy wooden frame and cushioned with cold-pressed foam that's enveloped in a soft fabric, this low-profile piece embodies relaxed luxury. Each plush cushion invites you to sink in and unwind, making it the perfect spot to lounge in style.

This contemporary sectional invites you to easily customize your space without the need for a full redesign, perfectly adapting to your needs and whims.

Rediscovered by a new generation of furniture enthusiasts, the Bellini has gained renewed adoration for its freedom and flexibility. Thanks to the clever design of tie rods and rings, you can effortlessly detach and reconfigure the modules, allowing the sofa to evolve with your tastes and moods.

Built with a sturdy wooden frame and soft fabric over cold-pressed foam, its low-profile design exudes a sense of laid-back luxury. Each plush cushion seems to call out for you to relax and unwind in style.

Perfect for open-plan living, this modern beauty allows you to transform your space according to your mood and needs, without the hassle of redecorating.

Once again adored by a new generation of furniture enthusiasts, the Bellini is celebrated for its versatility and liberating design. Thanks to its tie rods and rings, you can effortlessly detach and rearrange its modules, giving you the freedom to tailor the sofa to your changing tastes and whims.

Built with a sturdy wooden frame and cushioned with cold-pressed foam that's enveloped in a soft fabric, this low-profile piece embodies relaxed luxury. Each plush cushion invites you to sink in and unwind, making it the perfect spot to lounge in style.

Description:
The Tired Man Ottoman is a sumptuous piece perfect for enhancing any living room, perfectly designed to accompany the iconic Tired Man Chair. Taking inspiration from timeless 1930s designs, this ottoman captures the spirit of Danish design principles, providing not just a place to rest your feet but a cozy haven of style and comfort.

Echoing the chair's distinct style, the Tired Man Ottoman features a plush, curved design that harmoniously pairs with its counterpart to offer a full relaxation experience. Its skillfully upholstered fabric infuses sophistication into any space, making it a versatile element in your home decor.

The Tired Man Chair is a timeless piece that warmly invites weary individuals to indulge in ultimate relaxation. This celebrated chair, drawing inspiration from its original 1935 design, is a testament to comfort and elegance. It beautifully captures the essence of Danish design, which values simplicity, practicality, and a cozy atmosphere.

Notable for its curved, wrap-around backrest and plushly padded arms, this chair is designed to envelop you in its comforting hug. It's the perfect retreat for anyone looking to unwind and recharge. The title "Tired Man Chair" is spot-on, as it encourages you to sink into its soft cushions and momentarily forget the hustle and bustle of everyday life. This chair truly appreciates the need for rest and revival, allowing you to relax, let go, and watch your stresses softly fade away.

Name: Deux Lounge Chair, White Boucle
Description:
The Deux Lounge Chair perfectly captures the essence of modern design style and comfort. Wrapped in a plush boucle fabric, this chair delivers a textured, cozy feel that's perfect for relaxation. Its inviting warm white hue adds a refreshing touch, easily enhancing any contemporary living environment.

It blends effortlessly with both sophisticated and minimalist interiors. This chair isn't just a stylish seating choice; it becomes a striking focal point in any room.

Description:
Elevate your space with the Demi Bar Stool from 4orm4, where elegance meets exceptional design. This bar stool is the ultimate in luxury seating, perfect for those with a keen eye for sophistication and style. The Demi Bar Stool isn't just a piece of furniture; it's a work of art that brings a touch of grandeur to any room.

Name: Delphi Bowl Chair, Wheat Gray Cashmere Wool
Description:
The Delphi Bowl Chair presents a stylish twist on the timeless retro conversational chair, with a modern spin that's perfect for any setting. Its distinctive bowl-shaped design, paired with a movable circular cushion, ensures both exceptional comfort and a harmonious look that seamlessly fits into your decor.

This chic piece features a sleek matte black frame that enhances its sophistication, lending a contemporary and minimalist vibe to the overall design. The chair's inviting warm grey shade serves as a versatile neutral, effortlessly integrating into a range of interior styles for those looking to add an elegant yet practical touch to their home.

Name: Decelle Round Dining Table, Walnut, 130cm
Description: Discover the stunning Decelle dining table by 4orm4, a perfect example of how balancing opposing forces can lead to something truly beautiful. The Cella Dining Table is a stunning piece that blends form and function beautifully. Its pedestal design is truly eye-catching, featuring a narrow neck that gracefully expands beneath the tabletop, creating a surface that appears delicate yet is firmly supported by a strong base. For the tabletop, you have two exquisite choices: a sleek ceramic or a white translucent glass, each gorgeously balanced with a rich walnut base showcasing a natural grain pattern that highlights its sophisticated design.

You can select from two sizes to best fit your dining space, accommodating either four or six guests comfortably. Whether you opt for the smaller or the larger version, the Cella Dining Table is sure to infuse modern elegance into your home, making it ideal for both cozy dinners and festive gatherings.

Name: Bianca Sofa, Scarlet Wool
Description:
The Bianca Sofa is no ordinary piece of furniture; it's a standout in the world of design, merging function with a playful pop art flair. Its vibrant and bold aesthetic serves as a reminder of the impact design can have on our thoughts and feelings, sparking creativity and emotion.

Name: Belia Two Seater Sofa, White Boucle
Description:
Relive the spirit of the 1970s with the Belia, a modern sectional that brings a refreshing change to open-plan living spaces, steering away from bulky furniture. Its dynamic design lets you easily modify your setup to match your room's vibe, your mood, or your needs, all without the hassle of complete redecorating.

The Belia has found its way into the hearts of a new generation of furniture enthusiasts who appreciate its flexible and liberating qualities. Thanks to its clever tie rods and rings, you can detach and rearrange the modules effortlessly, allowing the sofa to evolve with your personal style and tastes.

Constructed with a sturdy wooden frame and wrapped in soft fabric over cold-pressed foam, its low-profile silhouette offers an inviting sense of laid-back luxury. Every plush cushion invites you to sink in and indulge in comfort.

Its dynamic design lets you easily modify your setup to match your room's vibe, your mood, or your needs, all without the hassle of complete redecorating.

The Belia has found its way into the hearts of a new generation of furniture enthusiasts who appreciate its flexible and liberating qualities. Thanks to its clever tie rods and rings, you can detach and rearrange the modules effortlessly, allowing the sofa to evolve with your personal style and tastes.

Constructed with a sturdy wooden frame and wrapped in soft fabric over cold-pressed foam, its low-profile silhouette offers an inviting sense of laid-back luxury. Every plush cushion invites you to sink in and indulge in comfort.

Relive the spirit of the 1970s with the Belia, a modern sectional that brings a refreshing change to open-plan living spaces, steering away from bulky furniture. Its dynamic design lets you easily modify your setup to match your room's vibe, your mood, or your needs, all without the hassle of complete redecorating.

The Belia has found its way into the hearts of a new generation of furniture enthusiasts who appreciate its flexible and liberating qualities. Thanks to its clever tie rods and rings, you can detach and rearrange the modules effortlessly, allowing the sofa to evolve with your personal style and tastes.

Constructed with a sturdy wooden frame and wrapped in soft fabric over cold-pressed foam, its low-profile silhouette offers an inviting sense of laid-back luxury. Every plush cushion invites you to sink in and indulge in comfort.

Relive the spirit of the 1970s with the Belia, a modern sectional that brings a refreshing change to open-plan living spaces, steering away from bulky furniture. Its dynamic design lets you easily modify your setup to match your room's vibe, your mood, or your needs, all without the hassle of complete redecorating.

The Belia has found its way into the hearts of a new generation of furniture enthusiasts who appreciate its flexible and liberating qualities. Thanks to its clever tie rods and rings, you can detach and rearrange the modules effortlessly, allowing the sofa to evolve with your personal style and tastes.

Constructed with a sturdy wooden frame and wrapped in soft fabric over cold-pressed foam, its low-profile silhouette offers an inviting sense of laid-back luxury. Every plush cushion invites you to sink in and indulge in comfort.

Its dynamic design lets you easily modify your setup to match your room's vibe, your mood, or your needs, all without the hassle of complete redecorating.

The Belia has found its way into the hearts of a new generation of furniture enthusiasts who appreciate its flexible and liberating qualities. Thanks to its clever tie rods and rings, you can detach and rearrange the modules effortlessly, allowing the sofa to evolve with your personal style and tastes.

Constructed with a sturdy wooden frame and wrapped in soft fabric over cold-pressed foam, its low-profile silhouette offers an inviting sense of laid-back luxury. Every plush cushion invites you to sink in and indulge in comfort.

Description:
The Baya Floor Lamp by 4orm4 is truly a standout piece, captivating attention with its unique design. It boasts glass spheres in a rich red-purple plum shade, topped with a frosted finish. Arranged in a whimsical cluster that brings to mind a bunch of grapes, these spheres inject a playful vibe into any room. The glass exteriors are adorned with delicate ridges, not only adding subtle texture but also gently diffusing the light to create a warm, ambient glow.

This artistic element is beautifully balanced by the sleek and sturdy metal stand, base, and fixtures, which offer a modern touch to the lamp's overall design. The fusion of elegance and originality makes the Baya Floor Lamp a perfect addition to any stylish space.

Name: Bao Three Seater Sofa, Emerald Velvet
Description:
The Bao Three Seater Sofa is perfect for those who want style without the hassle. This sofa comes dressed in easy-care velvet that boasts a rich and vibrant green, wonderfully complemented by a sturdy metal frame with a sleek gunmetal gray finish. The design showcases buttoned upholstery and thick piping details, adding a touch of elegance across the back and seat cushions. Its luxurious curved shape not only enhances comfort but also ensures a chic, modern look, providing ample seating that's sure to catch the eye.

With its armless, contemporary style, this sofa is an excellent fit for cozy living rooms or spaces where you love entertaining guests. To create a harmonious setting, team it up with the matching lounge chair from 4orm4, crafting a sophisticated suite that blends comfort with class.

Name: Bao Lounge Chair, Emerald Velvet
Description:
Meet the Bao Lounge Chair, a stylish addition to any room with its striking rich green velvet that's a breeze to maintain. Supported by a sturdy metal frame finished in a sleek gunmetal gray, this chair is as durable as it is elegant. The buttoned upholstery and thick piping detail give it a refined touch, while the sumptuous curves provide both comfort and style. With its generous seating and standout design, this chair is sure to become a focal point in any space.

Perfect for relaxed living rooms or entertainment areas, this armless contemporary lounge chair invites you to sit back and relax. Pair it with the matching sofa from 4orm4 for a seamless look that blends comfort with sophistication, creating a cohesive suite that's both inviting and chic.

Name: A330S Golden Bell Pendant Light, White
Description: The A330S Golden Bell Lamp is a stunning example of classic Scandinavian design, enchanting enthusiasts globally with its enduring elegance and inventive craftsmanship. Named for its unique, bell-shaped shade, this lamp is beautifully crafted to emit a warm, golden glow that radiates luxury and sophistication. A standout feature is the perforated ring at the bottom of the shade, which is both decorative and functional. This detail enables a soft, downward-directed light while also introducing a captivating visual texture to the piece.
